AUDIO: 'All the images that you\'re seeing right now were all generated with Ideogram 4 running locally in ComfyUI. And if you tried this model before and you were like, "Eh, it\'s too complicated or it\'s okay." I think I\'m going to need you to watch this video because you might be doing something wrong. I almost gave up'

